      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
        <docTitle refersTo="#adoption">Adopted by the Security Council at its <inline name="adoptionMeeting" title="5461st">5461st meeting</inline>, on<docDate date="2006-06-15" refersTo="#adoptionDate">15 June 2006</docDate></docTitle>
